  "description": [
    "THREE MAKE PLANS FOR DEFENSE OF REPUBLIC Teader Special Service HAMBURG The national con vention of the Socialist party of Germany here adopted resolutions for the defense of the republic for the liberation of schools from church rule for the right of civil servants to join political parties and labor unions The resolution concerning the re public and the present duties of the Socialist party in it is the most im portant It marks a definite policy of constructive social progress as the essential task of Socialist states men Workers Need Democracy Attempts to do away with the democratic republic having been de feated by the growing resistance of the masses the political and social reactionaries under the leadership of the German Nationalist party now try to restore the old regime of big landlords and capitalists by using the power of government the resolution begins The Nationalists for the present try to hide their monarehistie de signs against the republic and dem ocracy in order to secure the aid of other capitalist parties for the realization of the material socially reactionary aims of landlordism At the same time the increasing concentration of capital enables the capitalists to organize the national"
